== Introduction ==

The [[Basic_Writing/Authors |authors]] of this book for the most part are the graduate students in Theory of Basic Writing at [http://english.missouristate.edu/gradprograms.htm Missouri State University]. Others are welcome to contribute to the project or to suggest areas overlooked. Future classes in Theory of Basic Writing and current or future ENG 100 instructors will continue the project. This is still open to anyone interested in Basic Writing.     

----

